## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="c4585-102"><xref:System.Drawing.BufferedGraphicsManager>类允许您为图形实现自定义双缓冲。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4585-102">The <xref:System.Drawing.BufferedGraphicsManager> class allows you to implement custom double buffering for your graphics.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c4585-103">使用双缓冲的图形可以减少或消除因重绘显示图面而引起的闪烁。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4585-103">Graphics that use double buffering can reduce or eliminate flicker that is caused by redrawing a display surface.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c4585-104">此类有一个静态属性， <xref:System.Drawing.BufferedGraphicsManager.Current%2A> 该属性返回 <xref:System.Drawing.BufferedGraphicsContext> 当前应用程序域的主。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4585-104">This class has one static property, <xref:System.Drawing.BufferedGraphicsManager.Current%2A>, which returns the main <xref:System.Drawing.BufferedGraphicsContext> for the current application domain.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c4585-105"><xref:System.Drawing.BufferedGraphicsContext>类创建 <xref:System.Drawing.BufferedGraphics> 可用于绘制缓冲图形的实例。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4585-105">The <xref:System.Drawing.BufferedGraphicsContext> class creates <xref:System.Drawing.BufferedGraphics> instances that can be used to draw buffered graphics.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c4585-106"><xref:System.Drawing.BufferedGraphics>类没有公共构造函数，必须 <xref:System.Drawing.BufferedGraphicsContext> 使用其方法为应用程序域创建对象 <xref:System.Drawing.BufferedGraphicsContext.Allocate%2A> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4585-106">The <xref:System.Drawing.BufferedGraphics> class has no public constructor and must be created by the <xref:System.Drawing.BufferedGraphicsContext> object for an application domain using its <xref:System.Drawing.BufferedGraphicsContext.Allocate%2A> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c4585-107">可以 <xref:System.Drawing.BufferedGraphicsContext> 从静态属性中检索当前应用程序域的对象 <xref:System.Drawing.BufferedGraphicsManager.Current%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c4585-107">You can retrieve the <xref:System.Drawing.BufferedGraphicsContext> object for the current application domain from the static <xref:System.Drawing.BufferedGraphicsManager.Current%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property.</span></span>  
  
